---
title: One-Pot Vegetarian Chilli with Quinoa
description: Presenting to you another versatile HelloFresh ‘one-pot wonder’! This delicious dish has a bit of a twist - quinoa (yes, cooked in the same pot as the chilli)! It still contains all of the flavours you know and love but with some new earthy cinnamon tones, add to this some hearty kidney beans, and you have one very satisfying and nutritious meal. Go for it!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pot-vegetarian-chilli-with-q-35c73dd2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/one-pot-vegetarian-chilli-with-q-129649d5.pdf
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/one-pot-vegetarian-chilli-with-q-57da5a5577d68da67a8b4568
time required: 40 minutes
cuisine: Moroccan
course: main course
